name: SPRWL_77 [DAT/Dissolving Realities]
description: SPRWL_77 was a game area for cyberpunk aficionados, a desolate night map derived from memory scans of Tokyo recovered from old terminals.  After the corruption of fragment 492B29 all its AfterLife Guests shifted position, replacing the closest data set and losing connection to the central hub. SPRWL77, a 200-meter-long abandoned street. A forgotten inaccessible set of subroutines and data. The now eternal home of 2048 digitized post-human souls. By RubenFro - Twitter: @Ruben_Fro
